and for our services from companies subject to European data protection laws and also require us to increase our data processing capabilities in those jurisdictions at significant expense. Moreover, other countries outside of Europe (e.g. China, Brazil) have enacted or are considering enacting similar cross-border data transfer restrictions and laws requiring local data residency, which could increase the cost and complexity of delivering our services and operating our business.
